          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Full-service commercial construction for all business needs.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="group p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-accent-500/50 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 ease-out">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-50 text-accent-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">New Developments</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Ground-up development projects from planning to completion.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="group p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-accent-500/50 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 ease-out">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-50 text-accent-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
