        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Two decades of proven results in Nevada construction — licensed, insured, and trusted.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- License Badge -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-6 bg-accent-50 rounded-2xl border-2 border-accent-500/30">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-500 text-white rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
